e inconvenience as stated below. Overall stay was pleasant nonetheless.\r\n\r\nDisappointed about room readiness (clogged toilet) upon arrival. Service maintenance staff were not immediately available to address the issue in a timely manner. waited 30 min in the room, until the hotel staff decided to move us to another available room. ','2015-08-13',NULL,0),('55cdfc4bdb63fd08eccdc935',904482,5,'Convenient to San Francisco by car.  Safepark','Bill','Convenient by car to San Francisco.  Safe off street parking.  Very clean, recently remodeled.  Comfortable queen size beds.','2015-08-14',NULL,0),('55ce014c8ef33508ec79abaa',910225,1,'Motel nightmare\r\n','','Place is dirty staff ripped us off terrible experience !!! Noisy ','2015-08-14',NULL,0),('55ce2d55c9e0d508ec225365',918527,4,'Nice hotel and very close to the SF Airport','Nellie','Easy to get to and easy to get back on the freeway to either the SF Airport or to go north to the City itself.  This is a simple hotel... do not expect fancy amenities.  We also felt very safe there.','2015-08-14',NULL,0),('55cfa3940155d708ecba5f38',20191,4,' Nice eating, shopping nearby good location ','mary','Near fwy.  No wastebasket in shower/toilet room.  Very convenient for ferry to SF. ','2015-08-15',NULL,0),('55cfda0bbe33a008f0c37742',14553,3,'San Francisco Inn','','Parking is slim.  Stairs are very difficult for older adults.  There should be rails on both sides of the stairs.  Lost money on the soda machine.  ','2015-08-16',NULL,0),('55d0a9453fcf7b08fa8bdcac',18962,3,'SFSU','SFSU Dad','Over priced for what you get. Very basic. Not special. The breakfast is toast and coffee. Rooms are clean and decent size. If I don\'t need to be close to SFSU, I will not stay here','2015-08-16',NULL,0),('55d0fea4db63fd08ecf33620',438727,3,'Airport Hotel','Dawn','We had trouble finding the hotel late at night but once we did the room was, though a little worn, comfortable as was the bed. ','2015-08-16',NULL,0),('55d1f83f47734908f4340443',910225,4