t around town. Staff was excellent very attentive to needs and accommodating. Highly recommend!','2016-01-01',NULL,0),('56870baf03d7d011f67ca664',524164,5,'','','The front desk person whose name is Rose, she is so nice and helpful. We are very happy to stay at this hotel, and will recommend friend to stay here too.','2016-01-01',NULL,0),('56880d4991eced500c111b5c',25271,4,'Near Tanforan','bill','Nice facility near Tanforan and 380. Xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxc','2016-01-02',NULL,0),('56881de33aedb8432c856b74',918527,3,'Breakfast was a joke','Hooman','The room has a kitchen which is good for longer stays. But the breakfast was the worst I\'ve had (pack of oatmeal with water)! I would be better off and come prepared if they had no breakfast at all.','2016-01-02',NULL,0),('56894b0283b3335318a67fa2',360,4,'Comfortable, Quite & Great Location','Gary','We were very satisfied with our stay for New Years.  Great location, walking distance to union square and many restaurants.  Rooms were very clean.  Staff was friendly and will return in the future.','2016-01-03',NULL,0),('568982af9964285763b4cbcb',883306,2,'Not very clean','','Bedding was dirty, floors were dirty, shower did not work, although covered parking was advertised it is very limited & had to park on street and pay for meter\r\n','2016-01-03',NULL,0),('5689c2898c371c46cf5fa131',790530,1,'Smoking and hair','Lisa','I was booked a smoking room without my knowledge so the room reeked.  I went to get into bed and there were stray hairs all over the bed.  I called and requested a room change which they did, but would not move me from a smoking room as that is what Expedia booked me.  The next room still reeked and there appeared to be dried blood on the back of one of the pillows.  I chose to leave and sleep at the airport rather than try and sleep in a stinky, smoky room.  ','2016-01-04',NULL,0),('568a16a8603da63c7127f566',19842,3,'Close to Civic Center but..','','It is a 60\'s motel with not much updating. Noisy unless you a