r the rooms to get an update. Why do the beds have to be so hard\r\nOverall a very good experience','2016-06-08',NULL,0),('57583960aeec6b0b26de080b',50993,1,'The Motel 6 is in terrible condition. ','Worst Motel 6','Filthy exterior inclunding buildings, grounds, pool. Manager, Art was extremely rude. Desk staff had inefficient equipment, the key machine did not work; told us to use a.Post-It note instead of giving us a \"Do Not Disturb\" hanger. Undesirables were walking around, very uncomfortable for Motel guests.','2016-06-08',NULL,0),('57583a790328960b295db723',50993,1,'Filthy Motel 6 in Belmont, CA.','Motel 6 Yuck','The Manager Art was extremely rude and kept bragging that he was a cop for 15 years. Grounds and pool were disgusting. Rooms were minimal, even for a Motel 6, one wash cloth for two guests.','2016-06-08',NULL,0),('575844f54d7c8d0b26549e2f',7942,3,'Good motel for its price in the region','','The motel was comfortable and clean enough. It was not the best motel I have ever stayed in but it was reasonable for the price. ','2016-06-08',NULL,0),('5758535693cda40b27aaafc8',225819,4,'','','Stayed for 3 nights. Super location and nicely designed boutique hotel. ','2016-06-08',NULL,0),('575864c7e426dd0b2e16c69a',24620,4,'Great location but bathroom was too small.','','I stayed at the Inter Continental Mark Hopkins for more than a week and had the greatest of times.  The Hotel location and beautiful facilities are its greatest assets.  However, the bathroom - although clean and well equipped - was too small.  It did not have a counter or vanity in which to place the toiletries, etc.  This proved rather inconvenient. ','2016-06-08',NULL,0),('57587949d46b400b2ee1c57e',40682,3,'good location but noisy ','James ','The stay was great until a bug crawled on me when I was in bed.','2016-06-08',NULL,0),('5758d8a9435dd80b2688384c',11509,5,'Nice hotel at great location','KK','We were greeted by friendly staff. The room was big and could easily accommodate 3 adults.  It i