. ','2016-07-07',NULL,0),('577ed5c795608f0b4961b6bb',15135,3,'Good location.','Hazel','Nice place to stay because it os near airport and not far from the city. ','2016-07-07',NULL,0),('577ee2e4e7401f0b47c99f25',6666,5,'It was very close to a lot of good entertainment! ','','It was very close to restaurants, bars and stores, as well as close to China town and the Civic Center! It has close parking as well! ','2016-07-07',NULL,0),('577f099686a89c0b48760247',28502,4,'','l','The price of the room was fair, room was realy clean.\r\nBreakfast not so good for $20.00 per person, for that price could have eaten better somewhere else.','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577f28d60cd612150d177890',455591,3,'Nice hotel for the price','lisa','Good distance from airport. Breakfast reasonable. ','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577f35769684e30b4a2aa1fa',12345,1,'Misssing Ring','','I forgot my ring.  I called in to see if they found it.  They said they would call me if they did.  No urgent given to this.  I called twice to see if they have found it and was told she was busy and would get back to me.  I called again and she told me they found it and would overnight my ring to me.  Still no ring.  I called today to check on ring and no one knows about it.  No notes on my reservation nothing.  MY RING IS MISSING AND THE HOTElL KNOWS NOTHING.','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577f6caa0cd612150d919f42',5338,3,'','Frank','Vintage old and small very busy street not alot of staff working','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577f79bf86a89c0b48158fed',3308,3,'You get what you pay for! ','Debbie','Furniture are getting old. Carpet looks dirty, but room was clean.  The staff was very nice and accommodating! ','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577f8acd23b4170b4928f44f',7713,1,'','','Internet connection is terrible, on and off every 2 minutes. They stopped serving breakfast at 8:00am. Parking lot is very hard to get in or out. ','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577f90c886a89c0b48795553',5984,4,'Great location','Ann','The hotel is central to everything in San Francisco.  Great hotel: staff very friendly and accommodating, the continental breakfast in the morning was very diverse, room very kept and clean.','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577fb3c09395710b49800f81',790530,4,'','','Competitively priced 2 star hotel in location convenient to SFO, courteous staff, well maintained.','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577fb50923b4170b49780b9e',1047,5,'Great location.   ','','I enjoyed the stay.  The hotel was right in the wharf area and so very convenient to all tourist attractions.\r\n\r\nThe only thing I did not like was the fee of 57$ for parking overnight.   ','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577fbc4a0cd612150d3eae8a',42336,5,'Beautiful trail along the beach.','','Friendly staff, nice hotel. Delicious breakfast options.','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577fc1c523b4170b49986d79',23383,5,'Great Downtown SF location!','Brent','We love the Taj! Always consistently providing us with top level service.','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577fc2e786a89c0b4851fcc3',28502,2,'Nice hotel, close to the airport and freeway but .','disappointed','Don\'t rely on shuttle service if you have an early morning or late night flight.  They\'ll ask you to take a cab for $20.  Similarly don\'t expect to park free as a guest, overnight parking is $20!\r\n\r\nGiven that this hotel bills at a premium over other hotels in the area, it was a major disappointment.  Go elsewhere, save yourself $40.','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577fc8b186a89c0b486e6bd8',118232,1,'Bad bad bad','Maribel','The receptionist said I couldn\'t check in without giving my work information...it was weird and uncomfortable. The bed was so hard and very squeaky! Carpet had stains. Felt like a Motel 6!!!','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577fda1a86a89c0b48d770f0',2981,5,'','','The hotel is beautiful! such nice staff! the pool gets crowded by kids but by 10pm its empty for the adults, it closes at midnight which was greatly appreciated! the free breakfast was delicious! a lot of variety!','2016-07-08',NULL,0),('577fdfd45a68010b4923d867',24468,5,'Great 