ere!!!','2016-08-15',NULL,0),('57b2595f1abb170b5a50d530',15769,5,'','','The room was super small but the location was fantastic and amazing staff.','2016-08-16',NULL,0),('57b276ade8dbc30b27d1e363',476728,5,'Vacation ','D','Nice hotel, close to everything especially Pier 39.','2016-08-16',NULL,0),('57b27a6ecd33f80b58b208df',1515923,5,'Close to China town.','','Pleasant staff. Rooms wifi excellent and the location is perfect for tourists.','2016-08-16',NULL,0),('57b27b57e8dbc30b27dfe9e7',547988,4,'Free parking and breakfast! ','','Free parking and breakfast! I was perfect for our family ','2016-08-16',NULL,0),('57b27ce0e8dbc30b27e37704',890830,4,'Convinient location','','Nice hotel. Clean and in a convinient location. You can walk to many attraccions\r\n','2016-08-16',NULL,0),('57b27f078745fe0b5a35b310',41833,5,'Close to sanfransisco tourist spots.\r\n','jan','Liked hotels old world character. Coffee and cookies at reception. Helpful staff.\r\n\r\n','2016-08-16',NULL,0),('57b2827af169830b594dcceb',5425,2,'','','It is a old unkept hotel. Not a four star hotel as stated on Expedia. ','2016-08-16',NULL,0),('57b28778f169830b5955675d',51116,5,'Nice place','KUSUNM','All was very good. There was some noise from planes flying over head due to close proximity to Oakland Airport','2016-08-16',NULL,0),('57b294a68def200b27d3baa5',27274,5,'','','loved this place! recommend this hotel to everyone... love the detail to everything.','2016-08-16',NULL,0),('57b2aa80f7d85d0b0574a8f0',23581,5,'','','San Francisco is a beautiful city with a terrible homeless problem. The streets are literally filled with homeless. I never really felt comfortable. ','2016-08-16',NULL,0),('57b2b1f948d5350b067d263a',40682,3,'Was desperate. ','Jed','Had to change from a fleabag hotel to the travel lodge. Guy at the front desk was rude but the rest of the staff were lovely so it was pleasant enough. ','2016-08-16',NULL,0),('57b2ff62b32f690b06358e2c',547988,3,'Close to san fransico its just over the bay bridge'